{"text": "In October 2009 TD Group’s wholly owned subsidiary, TransDigm Inc., completed the offering of $425", "bbox": [204.2, 1079.9, 1074.8, 1100.7]}, {"text": "million of 73⁄4% Senior Subordinated Notes due 2014 at a discount, receiving net proceeds of $412.8 million.", "bbox": [162.5, 1104.1, 1076.8, 1125.7]}, {"text": "TransDigm Inc. used the net proceeds from the offering of the notes to make a cash distribution to TD Group", "bbox": [162.5, 1129.9, 1073.5, 1150.7]}, {"text": "which, in turn, made a special cash dividend to its stockholders of $7.65 per share and cash dividend equivalent", "bbox": [162.5, 1154.9, 1093.7, 1175.7]}, {"text": "payments (“Dividend Equivalent Payments”) to holders of options to purchase its common stock. The special", "bbox": [162.5, 1179.9, 1076.4, 1200.7]}, {"text": "cash dividend amounting to $374.6 million was paid on October 26, 2009 and the Dividend Equivalent Payments", "bbox": [162.5, 1204.9, 1107.9, 1225.7]}, {"text": "amounting to approximately $30.3 million were paid in October and November 2009.", "bbox": [162.5, 1229.9, 878.1, 1250.7]}, {"text": "The Company has evaluated the period beginning September 30, 2009 through November 24, 2009, the date", "bbox": [204.2, 1279.9, 1108.9, 1300.7]}, {"text": "the Company’s annual financial statements were issued, and concluded there were no other events or transactions", "bbox": [162.5, 1304.9, 1109.3, 1325.7]}, {"text": "occurring during this period that required recognition or additional disclosure in the financial statements.", "bbox": [162.5, 1329.9, 1038.0, 1350.7]}, {"text": "F-25", "bbox": [617.8, 1484.1, 657.2, 1504.9]}]}